'''热带风暴布雷特'''（{{lang-en|Tropical Storm Bret}}）于2011年7月17日在[[巴哈马|巴哈马]]以北的[[锋_(气象)|锋区]]西南边缘沿线发展形成，是[[2011年大西洋飓风季|2011年大西洋飓风季]]第二场获得命名的风暴。气旋起初的移动幅度很小，并因上层环境有利而逐渐增强，然后达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]110公里的最高强度。由于转向气流格局渐趋明朗，风暴转向东北，行经海域的[[风切变|垂直风切变]]有大幅增长。虽然受到风切变的不利影响，但接下来几天里布雷特的环流依然层次分明，中心附近还偶有[[对流|对流]]爆发。到了7月22日，气旋内已持续数小时没有强劲[[雷暴|雷暴]]，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]因此在系统行进至[[百慕大|百慕大]]以北约605公里洋面时停止针对布雷特发布公告。

风暴存在的大部分时间都位于大西洋开放海域上空，所以对陆地的影响有限。气旋早期的移动幅度很小，令巴哈马中北部大范围地区天气恶劣。布雷特还在[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]]东岸产生狂风，沿海地区波涛汹涌，导致多人受伤。虽然距离陆地还相当远，但风暴仍令百慕大上空的热带水份增强，当地旱情因此得到缓解。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Bret 2011 track.png}}
2011年7月中旬，有大范围上层[[低压槽|低压槽]]在西北[[大西洋|大西洋]]上空南下，从[[百慕大|百慕大]]一直延伸到[[乔治亚州|乔治亚州]]内陆上空的[[冷锋|冷锋]]因此得到强化<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWDAT/2011/TWDAT.201107150552.txt | title = Tropical Weather Discussion | date = 2011-07-15 | accessdate = 2016-04-16 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | last = Wallace | first = Patricia | location = [[迈阿密|Miami]], [[佛罗里达州|FL]] | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304032205/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWDAT/2011/TWDAT.201107150552.txt | deadurl = no | format = [[文本文件|TXT]] }}</ref>。锋区北侧大范围地区降下小雨，最西侧部分则在[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]]东北部上空基本保持静止状态<ref>{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWDAT/2011/TWDAT.201107160008.txt | title = Tropical Weather Discussion | date = 2011-07-15 | accessdate = 2016-04-17 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | last = Christensen | first = Eric | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304104842/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWDAT/2011/TWDAT.201107160008.txt | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | format = TXT | location = Miami, FL }}</ref>。7月16日，位于近海并且正在逐渐衰减的冷锋边缘沿线发展出[[低气压|地面低气压区]]<ref>{{cite report | last = Garcia | first = Felix | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | location = Miami, FL | format = TXT | title = Tropical Weather Discussion | date = 2011-07-15 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304141016/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWDAT/2011/TWDAT.201107161754.txt | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWDAT/2011/TWDAT.201107161754.txt | accessdate = 2016-04-17 | publisher = National Hurricane Center }}</ref>，还在[[巴哈马|巴哈马]]以北洋面产生稀疏[[对流|对流区]]<ref>{{cite report | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304051934/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201107161742/index.php?basin=atl | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201107161742/index.php?basin=atl | title = Graphical Tropical Weather Outlook | date = 2011-07-16 | accessdate = 2016-04-17 | publisher = [[美国国家海洋和大气管理局|National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration]] | work = National Hurricane Center | last = Stewart | first = Stacy | location = Miami, FL | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>。虽然内部起初缺乏环流，[[气压|地面气压]]也相对较高，但低气压区的组织结构还是在[[风切变|风切变]]逐渐消退的情况下得以改善<ref>{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201107170538/index.php?basin=atl | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304071130/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201107170538/index.php?basin=atl | title = Graphical Tropical Weather Outlook | date = 2011-07-16 | accessdate = 2016-04-17 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | last = Beven | first = Jack | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。[[飓风猎人|飓风猎人]]侦察机在[[阿巴科群岛|大阿巴科岛]]西北方向约160公里海域发现闭合环流中心，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]因此于[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]7月17日晚21点宣布有[[热带气旋|热带低气压]]形成<ref name="discuss1">{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al02/al022011.discus.001.shtml? | title = Tropical Depression Two Discussion Number One | date = 2011-07-17 | accessdate = 2016-04-17 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | last1 = Pasch | first1 = Richard | last2 = Stewart | first2 = Stacy | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304100025/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al02/al022011.discus.001.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | location = Miami, FL }}</ref>。成为热带气旋后，系统内的深层对流迅速增长，风力也不断提高，仅三小时后就升级成热带风暴并获名“布雷特”（{{lang|en|Bret}}）<ref>{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al02/al022011.discus.002.shtml? | title = Tropical Storm Bret Advisory Number Two | date = 2011-07-18 | accessdate = 2016-04-17 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | last1 = Brown | first1 = Dan | last2 = Berg | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160325113301/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al02/al022011.discus.002.shtml | first2 = Robbie | location = Miami, FL | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-25 }}</ref>。

气旋所在位置正处[[副热带高压脊|副热带高压脊]]的薄弱环节，布雷特因此在获名后的一段时间里以非常缓慢的速度南下<ref name="discuss1" />。虽然西侧有干燥空气逼近，但风暴继续强化，东部半圆有显著的深层[[雨带|雷暴带]]逐渐收紧<ref>{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al02/al022011.discus.003.shtml? | title = Tropical Storm Bret Advisory Number Three | date = 2011-07-18 | accessdate = 2016-04-17 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | last = Brennan | first = Michael | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306125119/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al02/al022011.discus.003.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-06 }}</ref>。7月18日，[[气象卫星|卫星图像]]显示系统内有结构混乱的[[风眼|眼状特征]]存在，表明布雷特的强度正快速增长。侦察机的观测结果也证实这一判断，风暴的下层风速已达到每小时110公里左右，只略低于飓风标准，这也是布雷特所达到的最高强度<ref name="TCR" /><ref>{{cite report | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306134923/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al02/al022011.discus.005.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al02/al022011.discus.005.shtml? | title = Tropical Storm Bret Discussion Number Five | accessdate = 2016-04-17 | date = 2011-07-18 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | last = Pasch | first = Richard | archivedate = 2016-03-06 }}</ref>。达到最高强度后，气旋因所在位置有[[高气压|高气压]]逐渐形成而开始加速朝东北方向前进，接下来数小时里强度的波动幅度都很小<ref>{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al02/al022011.discus.006.shtml? | title = Tropical Storm Bret Discussion Number Six | accessdate = 2016-04-17 | date = 2011-07-19 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | last = Berg | first = Robbie | archivedate = 2016-03-22 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160322112958/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al02/al022011.discus.006.shtml | deadurl = no }}</ref>，只是在外界存在强烈风切变，同时又缺乏热带湿气的双重不利因素下无法进一步增强。到了7月19日，布雷特的环流中心已经暴露出来，缺乏深层对流，风速降至每小时85公里，并且行经洋面的环境越来越不利于热带气旋发展<ref>{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al02/al022011.discus.007.shtml? | title = Tropical Storm Bret Discussion Number Seven | accessdate = 2016-04-17 | date = 2011-07-19 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | last = Brennan | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306130320/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al02/al022011.discus.007.shtml | first = Michael | archivedate = 2016-03-06 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。不过，这些不利条件还不足以令风暴强度快速下降，接下来两天气旋移动速度放缓，强度基本保持不变，下层环流依然层次分明，西南象限内也有数次持续性的雷暴爆发<ref>{{cite report | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304221538/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al02/al022011.discus.009.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al02/al022011.discus.009.shtml? | title = Tropical Storm Bret Discussion Number Nine | accessdate = 2016-04-17 | date = 2011-07-19 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | last = Brennan | first = Michael | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

7月20日清晨，结构已严重消退的布雷特因受西南气流逐渐加强影响而开始加快移动速度<ref>{{cite report | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160411072129/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al02/al022011.discus.011.shtml | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al02/al022011.discus.011.shtml? | title = Tropical Storm Bret Discussion Number Eleven | accessdate = 2016-04-17 | date = 2011-07-20 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | last = Cangialosi | first = John | archivedate = 2016-04-11 }}</ref>。接下来几天里，气旋结构持续退化<ref>{{cite report | archivedate = 2016-04-11 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160411072549/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al02/al022011.discus.014.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al02/al022011.discus.014.shtml? | title = Tropical Storm Bret Discussion Number Fourteen | accessdate = 2016-04-17 | date = 2011-07-20 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | last = Beven | first = Jack }}</ref><ref>{{cite report | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160317164443/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al02/al022011.discus.016.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al02/al022011.discus.016.shtml? | title = Tropical Storm Bret Discussion Number Sixteen | accessdate = 2016-04-17 | date = 2011-07-21 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | last = Beven | first = Jack | archivedate = 2016-03-17 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，但由于上层风出现短暂消退，暴露在外的中心以南又间歇爆发出对流<ref>{{cite report | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160411115705/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al02/al022011.discus.012.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al02/al022011.discus.012.shtml? | title = Tropical Storm Bret Discussion Number Twelve | accessdate = 2016-04-17 | date = 2011-07-20 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | last = Beven | first = Jack | archivedate = 2016-04-11 }}</ref><ref>{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al02/al022011.discus.015.shtml? | title = Tropical Storm Bret Discussion Number Fifteen | accessdate = 2016-04-17 | date = 2011-07-21 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | last = Stewart | first = Stacy | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303210941/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al02/al022011.discus.015.shtml | deadurl = no }}</ref>。7月22日，布雷特终于在[[海面温度|水温]]寒冷的洋面上空弱化成热带低气压，其前进速度逐渐加快，内部再度出现缺乏显著对流的情况<ref>{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al02/al022011.discus.018.shtml? | title = Tropical Depression Bret Discussion Number Eighteen | accessdate = 2016-04-17 | date = 2011-07-22 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | last = Pasch | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305010438/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al02/al022011.discus.018.shtml | first = Richard | archivedate = 2016-03-05 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。美国国家飓风中心指出，虽然外界环境极为不利，还受到强烈的风切变摧残，但气旋异常顽强，“拒不消散”，船只观测数据也表明布雷特仍在大范围海域产生大风<ref>{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al02/al022011.discus.019.shtml? | title = Tropical Depression Bret Discussion Number Nineteen | accessdate = 2016-04-17 | date = 2011-07-22 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | last = Stewart | first = Stacy | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304221654/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al02/al022011.discus.019.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>。但到了{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}这天下午15点，气旋的环流结构已经变得混乱，美国国家飓风中心宣布位于百慕大以北约605公里洋面的系统已不再属于热带气旋<ref>{{cite report | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304131651/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al02/al022011.discus.020.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al02/al022011.discus.020.shtml? | title = Post-Tropical Cyclone Bret Discussion Number Twenty | accessdate = 2016-04-17 | date = 2011-07-22 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | last = Beven | first = Jack | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。布雷特的残留低气压区在接下来几天里继续朝东北方向深入大西洋，直至7月23日完全消散<ref name="TCR" />。

== 防灾措施和影响 ==

=== 巴哈马 ===
[[File:Bret_Jul_22_2011_1735Z.jpg|thumb]]
热带低气压成形之际，百慕大政府向该国西北部多个岛屿发布[[热带气旋警告|热带风暴观察预警]]<ref>{{cite report |author=National Weather Service |date=2011-07-17 |accessdate=2016-04-17 |archivedate=2014-01-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140104001325/http://www.bahamaislandsinfo.com/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=9353%3Atropical-storm-watch-issued-for-abaco-and-grand-bahama&catid=93%3Abahamas-weather&Itemid=212 |url=http://www.bahamaislandsinfo.com/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=9353:tropical-storm-watch-issued-for-abaco-and-grand-bahama&catid=93:bahamas-weather&Itemid=212 |title=Tropical Storm Watch issued for Abaco and Grand Bahama |publisher=Bahama Islands Info |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，并在气旋呈现强化迹象时升级成热带风暴警告<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al02/al022011.public_a.002.shtml? | title = Tropical Storm Bret Advisory Number Two A | date = 2011-07-18 | accessdate = 2016-04-16 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160404200442/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al02/al022011.public_a.002.shtml | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | last = Brennan | first = Jack | archivedate = 2016-04-04 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。南面的[[新普罗维登斯岛|新普罗维登斯岛]]和[[安德罗斯岛|安德罗斯岛]]进入恶劣天气警告生效状态<ref name="tribune">{{cite news | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120315024542/http://www.tribune242.com/07182011_stormupdate_news_pg | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.tribune242.com/07182011_stormupdate_news_pg | title = Storm Update: Severe weather warning For New Providence and Andros | date = 2011-07-18 | accessdate = 2012-03-15 | newspaper = The Tribune | publisher = The Tribune | author = Staff writer | archivedate = 2012-03-15 }}</ref>，有关部门敦促船主固定好小型船只<ref>{{cite news | title = Alert No. 1 Tropical Depression No. 2 | date = 2011-07-17 | last = Dean | first = Basil A. | publisher = The Bahamas Meteorological Department}}</ref>。布雷特当天转向逐渐远离后，上述警告相应中止<ref>{{cite report | location = Miami, FL | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160403074153/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al02/al022011.public.005.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al02/al022011.public.005.shtml? | title = Tropical Storm Bret Advisory Number Five | date = 2011-07-18 | accessdate = 2016-04-17 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | last = Pasch | first = Richard | archivedate = 2016-04-03 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

风暴起初的移动速度非常缓慢，巴哈马北部大部分地区因此长时间阴云密布，并以[[大巴哈马岛|大巴哈马岛]]和阿巴科群岛天气最为恶劣<ref name="tribune" />。7月16至17日正逢周末，估计阿巴科群岛的降雨量达到75毫米<ref name="nassau">{{cite web | url = http://www.thenassauguardian.com/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=11668&Itemid=27 | title = Weather system dumps rain over parts of Bahamas | last = Robards | first = Chester | newspaper = The Nassau Guardian | publisher = The Nassau Guardian | date = 2011-07-19 | accessdate = 2016-04-17 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304064125/http://www.thenassauguardian.com/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=11668&Itemid=27 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。此外，岛上有气象站在风暴期间测得时速77公里的强烈阵风<ref>{{cite web |archiveurl=https://archive.li/20130210122757/http://www.wunderground.com/weatherstation/WXDailyHistory.asp?ID=IABACOEL1&month=7&day=18&year=2011 |url=http://www.wunderground.com/weatherstation/WXDailyHistory.asp?ID=IABACOEL1&month=7&day=18&year=2011 |title=History for IABACOEL1: Daily Summary for July 18, 2011 |publisher=Weather Underground, Inc |date=2011-07-18 |accessdate=2013-02-10 |archivedate=2013-02-10 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。降雨导致当地[[少年棒球联盟|少年棒球联盟]]的棒球赛事取消<ref name="nassau" />。布雷特的外围[[雨带|雨带]]催生出[[海龙卷风|海龙卷风]]并在[[天堂岛|天堂岛]]着陆，并伴有雷击和骤雨<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.bahamaslocal.com/newsitem/26739/Water_Spout_Touches_Down_on_Paradise_Island.html | title = Water spout touches down on Paradise Island | date = 2011-07-18 | accessdate = 2016-04-17 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303231302/http://www.bahamaslocal.com/newsitem/26739/Water_Spout_Touches_Down_on_Paradise_Island.html | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | publisher = Bahamas Local | author = Staff writer }}</ref>。总体而言，这场风暴对当地的影响利大于弊，降雨令各地旱情得到缓解<ref name="nassau" />。

=== 美国和百慕大 ===
受布雷特影响，佛罗里达州近海海况恶劣，有1.9米高的中浪<ref name="rip">{{cite news | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120402164749/http://www.news-journalonline.com/news/local/east-volusia/2011/07/20/storm-surf-expected-to-subside-but-not-rip-currents.html | accessdate = 2012-04-02 | archivedate = 2012-04-02 | 5 =  | url = http://www.news-journalonline.com/news/local/east-volusia/2011/07/20/storm-surf-expected-to-subside-but-not-rip-currents.html | title = Storm surf expected to subside but not rip currents | newspaper = The Daytona Beach News-Journal | author = Staff reporter | publisher = Halifax Media Holdings | date = 2011-07-20 }}</ref>，[[布里瓦德县_(佛罗里达州)|布里瓦德县]]有多人在游泳或冲浪时因遭遇大浪而受轻伤<ref>{{cite news | title = Tropical Storm Bret produces strong rip currents | last1 = Kavanagh | first1 = Margaret | last2 = Saenz | first2 = Saul | publisher = News 13 | date = 2011-07-19}}</ref>。强烈的[[离岸流|离岸流]]将数十人卷入大海，所幸他们很快便已获救，无人伤亡<ref name="rip" />。此外，海浪还把一些有毒的[[水母|水母]]冲上岸，多个海滩上共有200余人被刺伤<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.wesh.com/r/28597598/detail.html | title = Bret stirs up rip currents, jellyfish | author = WESH 2 News | publisher = Hearst Television | date = 2011-07-19 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120314091149/http://www.wesh.com/r/28597598/detail.html | accessdate = 2011-07-19 | archivedate = 2012-03-14 }}</ref>。据报道，海上还曾出现过多个[[漏斗云|漏斗云]]和海龙卷风，但都很快便已消散，没有对陆地产生影响<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.wptv.com/dpp/news/local_news/youreport/wptv-youreporter-spots-%27fire-funnel%27-clouds-in-stuart | title = WPTV YouReporter spots 'fire funnel' clouds in Stuart | publisher = WPTV-TV | last = Reynolds | first = Mollie | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140102230521/http://www.wptv.com/dpp/news/local_news/youreport/wptv-youreporter-spots-%27fire-funnel%27-clouds-in-stuart | date = 2011-07-18 | accessdate = 2014-01-02 | archivedate = 2014-01-02 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。整场风暴对陆地的影响很小，布里瓦德县和[[沃卢西亚县|沃卢西亚县]]在晨间降下小雨并伴随有微风<ref>{{cite news | publisher = Halifax Media Holdings | date = 2011-07-18 | accessdate = 2011-07-24 | archivedate = 2012-03-19 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120319172023/http://www.news-journalonline.com/news/outdoors/environment/2011/07/18/tropical-storm-bret-forms-off-florida-coast.html | title = Tropical Storm Bret forms off Florida coast | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.news-journalonline.com/news/outdoors/environment/2011/07/18/tropical-storm-bret-forms-off-florida-coast.html | work = The Daytona Beach News-Journal | last = Pulver | first = Dinah V. }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = Tropical Storm Bret to produce strong rip currents | date = 2011-07-18 | author = Staff writer | publisher = Central Florida Free}}</ref>。位于乔治亚州和佛罗里达州边界的[[奥克弗诺基沼泽|奥克弗诺基沼泽]]正发生大规模[[山火|山火]]<ref>{{cite web | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150425222051/http://www.gpb.org/news/2011/07/18/rains-hold-down-wildfire | archivedate = 2015-04-25 | url = http://www.gpb.org/news/2011/07/18/rains-hold-down-wildfire | title = Rain holds down wildfire | last = Treiguts | first = Edgar | publisher = GPB | date = 2011-07-18 | accessdate = 2016-04-17 }}</ref>，迫切需要降雨压制，但风暴向东北方向逐渐远离之际又带来大量干燥空气，降低出现降水的可能<ref>{{cite web | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140104001246/http://hurricanereport.blogs.heraldtribune.com/10909/florida-gets-dry-air-as-brett-begins-its-northeastward-move/ | title = Florida gets dry air as Brett begins its northeastward move | last = Spinner | first = Kate | date = 2011-07-18 | accessdate = 2014-07-21 | newspaper = Herald-Tribune | publisher = The New York Times Company | url = http://hurricanereport.blogs.heraldtribune.com/10909/florida-gets-dry-air-as-brett-begins-its-northeastward-move/ | archivedate = 2014-01-04 }}</ref>。

布雷特的前身曾在百慕大产生阵雨，但降雨量很小，24小时总计不超过22毫米<ref>{{cite report | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160417084641/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWDAT/2011/TWDAT.201107151748.txt | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWDAT/2011/TWDAT.201107151748.txt | title = Tropical Weather Discussion | date = 2011-07-15 | accessdate = 2016-04-17 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | last = Tichacek | first = Mike | archivedate = 2016-04-17 | format = TXT | deadurl = no }}</ref>。风暴带来的湿气对雨量推波助澜<ref>{{cite news | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304195644/http://bernews.com/2011/07/inclement-weather-beat-the-retreat-cancelled/ | url = http://bernews.com/2011/07/inclement-weather-beat-the-retreat-cancelled/ | title = Inclement weather: Beat the retreat cancelled | date = 2011-07-20 | accessdate = 2016-04-17 | newspaper = Bernews | publisher = Bernews.com | author = Staff writer }}</ref>，百慕大持续数月的旱情至此告终。7月18日，[[L.F.韦德国际机场|百慕大国际机场]]降下45毫米雨量，而且次日又测得40毫米降水。这些降雨对该国总体有利，但也对部分排水条件不佳的企业或商铺构成不利影响。<ref>{{cite news | title = Island sees heavy rainfall after several dry months | first = Owain | publisher = The Bermuda Press | url = http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20110720/NEWS07/707209999/0 | date = 2011-07-20 | accessdate = 2016-04-17 | newspaper = The Royal Gazette | last = Johnston-Barnes | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304203142/http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20110720/NEWS07/707209999/0 }}</ref>

